These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, writing, woodworking, skydiving
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, purple, brown, red
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person who likes purple is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who likes brown is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person who likes purple is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Hobby   | writing    | skydiving    | dancing      | woodworking    |
| Color   | red | purple | brown | coral |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

