.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, azalea, rose
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, billiard, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who growsrose is between the owner of the frog and the person playing backgammon##2
6. the person playing snooker is between the person who growsrose and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Flower   | poppy      | daisy  | rose  | azalea |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Game         | canasta    | snooker | billiard | backgammon |

