.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, superhero, fantasy, comedy
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bolivar, montecristo, bluemaster
1. the paramedic is the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the lawyer is the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
9. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person eating lemon and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Movie-Genre       | superhero   | thriller   | fantasy | comedy |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Cigar   | montecristo    | bolivar | prince  | bluemaster    |

