.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry, potato, garlic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, card-games, baking, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating pomegranate##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating potato##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person eating raspberry is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person eating garlic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Food           | pomegranate  | garlic | raspberry     | potato |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Hobby           | card-games       | photography    | baking      | singing           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

