 3. the security-guard is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the lawyer is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the fan of rock and the person who growsamaryllis##2
10. the person who growssunflower is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
