The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
House: victorian, cape-cod, craftsman, tower
1. the fan of folk is between the tower house and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person driving the van is between the fan of folk and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the cape-cod house and the dutch##2
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the craftsman house##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person driving the train##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Transport           | boat | van | train  | taxi |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| House         | craftsman   | tower    | victorian | cape-cod   |

