The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing, photography, camping
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, fanta, 7up
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person drinking fanta##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Hobby   | puzzles   | photography   | camping | fishing |
| Beverage     | coffee    | 7up   | hot-chocolate    | fanta  |

