3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the cain-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Cigar      | fonseca  | aristoff   | cain    | swisher  |
