 2. the person eating tomato is the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the fisherman is the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the person traveling to colone is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the person who growsdaffodil##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| Job           | social-worker | accountant | designer   | fisherman |
| City   | marseilles         | rome       | colone      | hamburg     |
