The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, spy, mystery, romance
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, june, july
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching mystery movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre       | crime        | romance       | mystery       | spy     |
| Birthday      | june | march | july | april        |
| Pet        | horse       | turtle     | rat         | dog           |

